  "session": "2026RS",
  "identifier": "HB 214",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to disabled veterans.",
  "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 40 to define terms; create the Residential Ease of Access for Disabled Veterans Program for funding the construction and installation of accessibility ramps on residences of disabled veterans; establish the Residential Ease of Access for Disabled Veterans Program grant fund to be used for the program and administered by the Kentucky Department of Veterans' Affairs.",
